  "title": "Highbury bore me",
  "sourceFile": "Waste_notes/highbury_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Highbury\n        bore me ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. <i>Purgatorio</i>, V. 133: </p>\n<p>\"Ricorditi di me, che son la Pia;<br/>\n        Siena mi fe', disfecemi Maremma.\" <a href=\"ricordit_T.htm\"><img alt='Italian: \"Remember me, who am La Pia / Siena made me, Maremma undid me.\"' src=\"..\\images\\T.gif\"/></a> [Eliot's note] <i>Highbury</i>:\n        aresidential London suburb; <i>Richmond</i>: a pleasant\n        part of London westward up the Thames, with boating and\n        riverside hotels. <i>Kew</i>: adjoining Richmond, has the\n        famous Kew Gardens.  </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>Purgatory, V.133</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Highbury bore me ... Cf. Purgatorio , V. 133: \"Ricorditi di me, che son la Pia; Siena mi fe', disfecemi Maremma.\" [Eliot's note] Highbury : aresidential London suburb; Richmond : a pleasant part of London westward up the Thames, with boating and riverside hotels. Kew : adjoining Richmond, has the famous Kew Gardens. Purgatory, V.133 back to \"The Waste Land\"",
